quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  26,53,Pharaoh sent to oppidum callers
  26,54,(Proclaiming) Hoc est parvulus gang
  26,55,They statim opposing nos
  26,56,all beware de them
  26,57,Consequently nos deprived them de gardens fons
  26,58,Ac treasures ac prenobilis position
  26,59,Tunc nos factus it inheritance Infans Israel
  26,60,They pursued them east
  26,61,When ambo parties vide each alius Moses' people dictus Nos caught
  26,62,He non dictus via My Dominus est me; He guide me
  26,63,Nos tunc inspired Moses Strike sea tuus staff whereupon it parted Each part est major collis
  26,64,Nos tunc delivered them totus
  26,65,Nos sic saved Moses totus those est eum
  26,66,Nos drowned others
  26,67,Hoc est sufficient proof multus people non est believers
  26,68,multus assuredly tuus Dominus est Almighty Merciful
  26,69,Narrate to them Abraham's history